Uttar Pradesh
Oct 13, 2014
Abuse
Description:
			An 18-year-old girl was allegedly raped by her neighbour, who also set her on fire after the crime in Faridpur area here today. 

The incident took place this afternoon when the girl was alone in her home and neighbour, Kantu, not only raped her but also set her on fire in Khemunagla village, police said. 

She was rushed to a nearby hospital and her condition is critical. 

Superintendent of Police (rural), Brijesh Srivastava, said that an FIR has been registered in the matter and the accused is being searched by the police.

